1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,540
Google just made a new AI model. It is a smart computer brain that learns from the internet.

2
00:00:05,839 --> 00:00:11,480
Imagine you have a friend who knows everything and can help you with anything. That is this AI!

3
00:00:11,779 --> 00:00:18,879
It reads tons of books, websites, and videos. Then it learns how to talk and solve problems.

4
00:00:19,179 --> 00:00:24,059
You can ask it to write a poem about a cat. It will make a new poem just for you in seconds.

5
00:00:24,359 --> 00:00:31,559
It does not just copy stuff. It mixes what it learned to make new ideas, like a chef making a new recipe.

6
00:00:31,859 --> 00:00:37,859
This helps you with homework or fun projects. But always think for yourself too.

7
00:00:38,159 --> 00:00:44,459
So Google’s new AI is a tool to boost your creativity. It is like a super-powered helper.

8
00:00:44,759 --> 00:00:49,839
Try asking it a fun question with a grown-up. See what amazing thing it creates!

